Collections.rule:
Individual: @A*
Types: Customer
Facts: foaf:firstName @B*(["(\S+)"]), 
         foaf:lastName @B*(["\S+\s(\S+)"]),
         email @C*,
         phone @G*,
         hasLocation @A*(mm:replace("cus", "loc"))

Individual: @A*
Types: Shop
Facts: foaf:name @B*, 
         supportEmail @C*,
         supportPhone @D*,
         currency @E*,
         status true,
         canAcceptOrder true,
         canDeliverOrder true,     
         canScheduleOrder true,        
         hasDeliveryGuy @A*(mm:replace("del", "man")),
         hasManager @A*(mm:replace("shop", "man")),
         hasLocation @A*(mm:replace("shop", "loc"))

Individual: @A*(mm:prepend("order_"))
Types: Order
Facts: 
totalPrice @D*(xsd:double),
taxPrice @D*(xsd:double),
deliveryPrice @D*(xsd:double),
hasCustomer @A*(mm:prepend("cus_")),
hasContact @A*(mm:prepend("cus_")),
hasOrganization @A*(mm:prepend("store_")),
hasDeliveryLocation @A*(mm:prepend("loc_")),
hasProduct @B*(mm:prepend("prod_"))

Individual: @A*(mm:prepend("price_"))
Types: Price
Facts: hasProduct @A*(mm:prepend("prod_")),
price @J*(xsd:double)

Individual: @A*
Types: Store
Facts: foaf:name @B*, 
         supportEmail @C*,
         supportPhone @D*,
         currency @E*,
         status true,
         canAcceptOrder true,
         canDeliverOrder true,     
         canScheduleOrder true,        
         hasDeliveryGuy @A*(mm:replace("del", "man")),
         hasManager @A*(mm:replace("store", "man")),
         hasLocation @A*(mm:replace("store", "loc"))

Individual: @N*
Types: Product
Facts: foaf:name @I*,
hasBrand @M*(mm:prepend("brand_")),
hasOrganization @L*(mm:prepend("shop_")),
hasWeightType @K*(mm:prepend("weight_")),
hasCategory @B*(mm:prepend("category_")),
hasPrice @A*(mm:prepend("price_")),
basePrice @J*(xsd:double),
stock @E*(xsd:double),
description @G*,
details @G*,
barCode @D*,
itemCode @C*

Individual: @A*(mm:replace("cus", "loc"))
Types: Location
Facts: city @D*, 
          country @E*, 
         addressline1 @F*,
         latitude @H*(xsd:double),
         longitude @I*(xsd:double)
